      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "Convex backend\n\nHTTP routes\n  POST /api/cli/mint-token\n  GET  /api/cli/sync\n  POST /webhooks/clerk\n\nQueries / Mutations / Actions\n  subscriptions.{queries, mutations, actions}\n  refreshLog.queries  (paginated)\n  machineActivity.queries (paginated)\n  cli.actions.{startLink, recordLogin}\n\nCron\n  refreshExpiringSubs\n  fetchUsageSnapshot\n\nTables\n  users   subscriptions(ciphertext+nonce)\n  refreshLog   machineActivity\n\nEnv: VAULT_AES_KEY  CLERK_SECRET_KEY",
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "convex",
      "originalText": "Convex backend\n\nHTTP routes\n  POST /api/cli/mint-token\n  GET  /api/cli/sync\n  POST /webhooks/clerk\n\nQueries / Mutations / Actions\n  subscriptions.{queries, mutations, actions}\n  refreshLog.queries  (paginated)\n  machineActivity.queries (paginated)\n  cli.actions.{startLink, recordLogin}\n\nCron\n  refreshExpiringSubs\n  fetchUsageSnapshot\n\nTables\n  users   subscriptions(ciphertext+nonce)\n  refreshLog   machineActivity\n\nEnv: VAULT_AES_KEY  CLERK_SECRET_KEY",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 14
    },
