      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "Flows:  (1-4) login = browser-assisted Clerk OAuth → signInToken POSTed to localhost.  (5) CLI → Convex HTTP/RPC for mint + sub CRUD.  Cron in Convex calls Anthropic for OAuth-token refresh + usage.  Webhook: Clerk user.* → /webhooks/clerk → users table.\nEncryption: subscriptions.ciphertext is AES-GCM under VAULT_AES_KEY (server-only).  CLI never sees the master key.  Local Keychain stores the active credential blob (single-slot, mirrors Claude Code).",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Flows:  (1-4) login = browser-assisted Clerk OAuth → signInToken POSTed to localhost.  (5) CLI → Convex HTTP/RPC for mint + sub CRUD.  Cron in Convex calls Anthropic for OAuth-token refresh + usage.  Webhook: Clerk user.* → /webhooks/clerk → users table.\nEncryption: subscriptions.ciphertext is AES-GCM under VAULT_AES_KEY (server-only).  CLI never sees the master key.  Local Keychain stores the active credential blob (single-slot, mirrors Claude Code).",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 12
    }
  ],
